text: Eurotrash could mean: * Eurotrash (term), a sometimes pejorative term referring to a particular American stereotype of Europeans * Eurotrash (TV series) * A pejorative term for Eurodance or Europop * "Eurotrash Girl", a song by Cracker (band) * "Euro Trash Girl", a song by Chicks on Speed * "Eurotrash", a song and album by Zeromancer
title: Eurotrash
